Time Frame for Completion

It is believed that a period of approximately two days will be
required to complete the dental inventories at each MR facility. In addition,
approximately three weeks will be required to complete each written report
and to prepare it for presentation for review to the facility, the Regional
Office and the Central Office of Mental Retardation. These time frames are
based on the experience of the review teams who completed the initial Dental
Reports for Cresson and Ebensburg Centers.

