Projected Cost

A cost of $250 per day plus expenses will be required for the
dentist completing the reviews. Allowing this cost for a two—day review
plus an appropriate amount for expenses, it would indicate that each
facility inventory will cost an average of $600. The ten reviews will,
therefore, cost an estimated $6,000. The specific amount for each facility
will depend on the amount of expenses involved in travel lodging.

The dentist will be paid by contract with the Department out of
Appropriation 40 funds. It would be suggested that each facility inventoried
be responsible for assuming the cost of the dentist for the reviews completed
there. .

